[normal]a 
[normal]proposal 
[normal]for 
[normal]‘County Deals
[normal].
[normal]’
[normal] The research argued that t
[normal]he 
[normal]G
[normal]overnment’s current approach
[normal] to fiscal devolution
[normal] 
[normal]create
[normal]s 
[normal]a real danger that the full
[normal] growth
[normal] potential of the county areas not involved in the 
[normal]S
[normal]econd 
[normal]W
[normal]ave of 
[normal]C
[normal]ity 
[normal]D
[normal]eals will not be exploited to the full. 
[normal]Shared Intelligence
[normal] recommend that 
[normal]a first wave of 
[normal]ambitious 
[normal]local growth deals covering county areas
[normal] should
[normal] be negotiated
[normal]. This would test how this type of deal might be developed and negotiated in the different types of economic geography and institutional configurations that exist in county areas.
