[normal]2.9
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Economically,
[normal] there is little justification for the
[normal] 
[normal]exclusion 
[normal]of counties from fiscal devolution
[normal]. 
[normal]Counties are 
[normal]not simply
[normal] ‘hinterland
[normal]s
[normal]’ 
[normal]bordering Cities. 
[normal]Statics show
[normal] they
[normal] outperform the Core Cities
[normal] and metropolitan boroughs
[normal] on a number
[normal] key indicator
[normal]s 
[normal](tables provided in Appendix
[normal] 3
[normal]), 
[normal]potentially providing a
[normal] better return on investment for Government funds and improved economic outcomes; 
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]CCN member council
[normal] areas
[normal] generat
[normal]e
[normal] over half of all GVA outside of London
[normal] (ONS, 2012)
[normal];
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]C
[normal]ounty areas 
[normal]contribute more GVA per head of population than many of the 
[normal]C
[normal]ore 
[normal]C
[normal]ities
[normal] (
[normal]ONS, 2012)
[normal]; 
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
