[normal] (ONS, 2012)
[normal];
[normal]-
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]CCN 
[normal]member areas
[normal] have the largest number of new enterprises created amongst 
[normal]all local authority types
[normal] (ONS, 2012)
[normal];
