[normal]2.10
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]There 
[normal]is
[normal] evidence from across CCN member councils that broader based and more ambitious fiscal devolution policies
[normal] could 
[normal]enable
[normal] 
[normal]counties
[normal] to be
[normal]tter
[normal] invest in 
[normal]local economies
[normal] and promote 
[normal]growth
